description:
In this edition of James CorTrend, Miles and super producer Becca discuss Rihanna's rumored song for the Black Panther 2 soundtrack, Instagram stealing from MySpace?, Brittney Griner spending her 32nd birthday in Russian prison, Trump's Special Master asking "where's the beef?", a student debt relief update,  and James Corden getting banned from Balthazar for being an asshole!
